Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:13.97,Formal,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(636,144)}Takasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, you're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I-In... Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've raised Ryuuji-kun well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I-I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why my life was in "danger"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Listen, Ya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After falling for the fake voicemail that Taiga left,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko cried a lot and Grandpa scolded her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, it's like Ya-chan is a child right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Families are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they haven't seen each other in about ten years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of you spoiling Yasuko{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, there's nothing wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.53,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a family, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji-kun, hurry up and take your bath before the water gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you weren't married...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad ran away with another woman while I was pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though everyone told me to get an abortion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I couldn't protect you and things broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Grandma say you raised me well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I'm a lot taller than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your back was really big when you were running...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So big that I didn't recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was also a little happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was so afraid that you'd leave and never come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you left by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the last person who should say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but running away won't get you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it right in front of you, not in some place far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you have to look at me... always.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma said there's nothing wrong with sleeping in the same room since we're going to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I understand how Yasuko became the way she is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya-chan is laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, turn off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I'm kind of worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:05:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think running away and getting married will work out,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I still want to have this dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like if I don't do something here, things will break again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you and Yasuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing broke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it's okay for us to start here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to run away to get married. Let's do it with everyone's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be best to receive everyone's blessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you mean by "everyone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, Grandma and your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will take a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we'll be happy anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why not share our happiness with everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but before that, let's have a little rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a veil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I, Takasu Ryuuji, will...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter, just say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can it not matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... will marry Aisaka Taiga{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, I don't want a vow yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Wasn't this your idea in the first{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what you said before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Since ancient times, the dragon has been the only beast to equal the tiger."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, even without a vow, we'll always be together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tai{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are red.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your breathing is all weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your lips are cracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll hurt if we kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we kiss, it'll definitely hurt... a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like a rough, dry wilderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it was really, really warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's cold, so let's do it one more{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.87,Formal,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(630,154)\c&H5F749D&}Takasu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, it feels weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just two of us left,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now three people and a pet are coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, you believed it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Ya-chan would come if you lied,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then get back on good terms with Grandma and Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think she would,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't think she wouldn't either...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps families are like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-chan, you're coming over for dinner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a family of three, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot about you, Inko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:00.89,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go ahead, I'm going to go change my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But won't your parents be{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quick, since I'm making your favorite tonight; pork cutlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, what are you think{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously don't think about the consequen{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it ou{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga... do you really hate me that mu{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving, so do whatever you want! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just like a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought that I would never be loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not just making pork cutlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma taught me how to make some delicious taro rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ryuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but perhaps that was just an excuse for running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see the stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so small...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:11:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hidden and lonely, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I blamed my lack of confidence on my parents and my surroundings,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Ryuuji still loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run away anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to accept everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be proud of myself and love Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:34.00,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, Taiga didn't come over for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, we can't understand if you don't tell us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What actually happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Taiga{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everyone, back to your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some bad news for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to family reasons, Aisaka-san is withdrawing from this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:12:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just received that message from her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san will be going back to her mother's{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx301.8868}-{\fscx100.62893} This is a lie, right? It's a joke, right? She was forced, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't tell us or...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your lives, you will all come to different crossroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of if you decide to stay where you are or turn back,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you still have to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san's decision may mean leaving you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's a decision she tried her best to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's support her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids these days are so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all calling Aisaka-san? Texting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should all take a good, hard look at your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.53,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.74,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't go through if we all call at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}Everyone, back to your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushie{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:01.00,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you clench your teeth for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come back by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Taiga transferring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takas{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I didn't want her to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd bring her back right now if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd ask her why she decided everything by herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she believes in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the only thing I can do right now is accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she learns how to be tidy at the last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A single sock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your buddy? I'll definitely find him for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That clumsy girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she forget these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.94,Formal,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz355\c&HAB9576&\fs12\pos(744,179)}One new message \Nfrom Taiga
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:44.78,Formal,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\frz353\pos(589,211)\c&HC2B2A3&}You never told me \Nthat you love me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember when I fell into the river{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was interrupted...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, I even said it a few times to Kawashima...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.29,Formal,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(427,373)\c&HA7887A&}Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can be really stupid sometimes too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomiya-kun, are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's somewhere I want to go, can you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry for yesterday."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I kind of understand what you said now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Taiga's text message!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:15:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like Taiga replied to everyone who texted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it just a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seaweed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that small dot a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You're imagining things, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's definitely a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did she take a picture of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will protect you all from the faraway sky."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! She's not dead yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she means, "I'll try my best."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even if the sky is pitch black, with nothing to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there will be stars shining somewhere out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep shining brighter and brighter,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely look better to people."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Taiga is kind of selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if that's the case, the sky will connect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we all shine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how far apart we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will definitely be able to see each other doing our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You overdid that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sent chills down my spine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the feeling of being young, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! I'll be happy if she's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of stars, someone caused a lot of trouble back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After taking the time to send us this, I think she'd be happy if we replied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember putting it away with Ami-chan's tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think of these things to make others happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it... You're amazing at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My existence itself should be surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, before she became who she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people loved her even though she caused trouble for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was jealous of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she seems amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her body and heart are both so small and timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All she does is take whatever people throw at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't let anyone see her true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the same as {\i1}someone{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she was seen through from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say I was a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I hate myself when I pretend to be an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm desperate to have others accept me for who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I finally understood after meeting Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there's at least one person who understands me, I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it isn't love...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I just have to press here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, please hurry up before my godlike power runs out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Takasu-kun. Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-min.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:38.86,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.57,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:46.33,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Since ancient times, the dragon has been the only beast to equal the tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:49.75,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're not by my side right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:55.21,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leap through space and time and always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:59.13,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,These feelings will never change.
