Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Inko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this makeup a bit much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a mother, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should just use some softer colors...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inko-chan finally said his own name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.86,Formal,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(712,48)\fs20\c&HC0BDB4&}Oohashi High School\N78th Graduation Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be lonely once the seniors leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all so cool and interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that our student council president, Kitamura-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be studying abroad in America after graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The president and the seniors made the Cultural Festival and the Sports Festival amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that the previous cultural festival was even more amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I heard about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the legendary one where 2-C won everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It was all because of the Palmtop something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Palmtop something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the Palmtop Tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who brings you good luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person really exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the Palmtop Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went to this school last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, she's Takasu-senpai's girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something in this world that no one has seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is gentle and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if it could be seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone would fight over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why no one has ever seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world hid it so that no one could get their hands on it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, someday, someone will find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who deserves it the most will definitely find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to surprise you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.30,0:22:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a millimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.31,0:22:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:22:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tai{\fscx301.8868}-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why would you say something embarrassing like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've waited for a better mood or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it's created.
